    "ProteinDT [249] combined the contrastive learning and autogressive and diffusion generative paradigm.",
    "These methods involve incorporating both inter-and intra-modality generative or constrative tasks to mutually enhance each other's effectiveness.2) Adaptation: The adaptation methods in MFMs also enrolled the FT, AT, and PE methods for their widely applications in healthcare practices.",
